videos.description: Willie Cauley-Stein goes down the lane and throws down the monster dunk, firing up the bench and owner Mark Cuban.

videos.headline: Cuban fired up after Cauley-Stein slam

videos.description: Trey Burke knocks down a 3-pointer to give the Mavericks a 50-point lead, the largest halftime margin in NBA history.
